Saved!
Job Details
Exciting ICT business is seeking a highly motivated, experienced and result oriented Telesales person.   If interested, please send your CV to hr@ixtel.com.  Please note that due to high volume of responses; only short listed candidates will be contacted.
Requirements
The ideal candidate will be fluent in English and preferably in Arabic, have at 3-4 years of Call Centre / Telesales experience, have excellent interpersonal skills and be able to bring in new business and retain it while generating additional business from existing customers. He/she should be able to achieve sales targets and is self-motivated and performance driven.
